OL,3,CITV News joins other UK journalists
OL,4,Ccalling for access to Gaza
OL,6,FITV News has joined a group of UK
OL,7,Fbroadcasters calling for "free and
OL,8,Funfettered access" to Gaza for foreign
OL,9,Fmedia to report on the war.
OL,11,FA group of 55 journalists have sent an
OL,12,Fopen letter to the embassies of Israel
OL,13,Fand Egypt in which they also appeal
OL,14,Ffor better protection for reporters
OL,15,Falready in the territory.
OL,17,FEntry into the enclave has to date
OL,18,Fbeen monitored and supervised by the
OL,19,FIsraeli military.
