OL,3,CITV News joins other UK journalists
OL,4,Ccalling for access to Gaza
OL,6,FITV News Senior International
OL,7,FCorrespondent John Irvine was able to
OL,8,Freport from Gaza in November, taken by
OL,9,Fthe Israeli Defence Forces (IDF) into
OL,10,Fthe heart of Gaza city to and to the .
OL,12,FIn the letter, journalists wrote:
OL,13,F"Almost five months into the war in
OL,14,FGaza, foreign reporters are still
OL,15,Fbeing denied access to the territory,
OL,16,Foutside of the rare and escorted trips
OL,17,Fwith the Israeli military.
OL,19,F"We urge the governments of Israel and
OL,20,FEgypt to allow free and unfettered
OL,21,Faccess to Gaza for all foreign media.
