OL,3,CITV News joins other UK journalists
OL,4,Ccalling for access to Gaza
OL,6,F"We call on the government of Israel
OL,7,Fto openly state its permission for
OL,8,Finternational journalists to operate
OL,9,Fin Gaza and for the Egyptian
OL,10,Fauthorities to allow international
OL,11,Fjournalists access to the Rafah
OL,12,FCrossing."
OL,14,FThe letter continued: "There is
OL,15,Fintense global interest in the events
OL,16,Fin Gaza and for now the only reporting
OL,17,Fhas come from journalists who were
OL,18,Falready based there.
