OL,3,CITV News joins other UK journalists
OL,4,Ccalling for access to Gaza
OL,6,F"It's vital that local journalists'
OL,7,Fsafety is respected and that their
OL,8,Fefforts are bolstered by the
OL,9,Fjournalism of members of the
OL,10,Finternational media. The need for
OL,11,Fcomprehensive on the ground reporting
OL,12,Fof the conflict is imperative.
OL,14,F"The risks of conflict reporting are
OL,15,Fwell understood by our organisations
OL,16,Fwho have decades of experience of
OL,17,Freporting in warzones around the world
OL,18,Fand in previous wars in Gaza."
